data.description: Welcome to 907 Teague Ave, nestled in the heart of Driggs, Idaho, where mountain vistas meet small-town charm. This property offers an unparalleled opportunity to own a slice of this sought-after area, renowned for its stunning natural beauty and abundant recreational opportunities.  Situated on a spacious acre of land, this home boasts a walkout basement, an attached garage, and a fenced yard, providing both convenience and privacy.  While the home may require some TLC to complete the basement and touch up certain areas, the potential is endless. With a little creativity and vision, this property could be transformed into the ultimate mountain retreat or investment opportunity.  Driggs itself is a magnet for outdoor enthusiasts, offering world-class skiing, hiking, fishing, and more, just minutes from your doorstep. Additionally, the town's vibrant community, charming downtown area, and proximity to Grand Teton and Yellowstone National Parks make it a destination that draws people in from far and wide.  Whether you're seeking a second home, a vacation getaway, or a short-term rental investment, this property ticks all the boxes. Don't miss your chance to own a piece of Driggs paradise at 907 Teague Ave.
